# Malaise Medic

## Class Overview
**Role:** Support healer / Resilient medic  
**Primary Ability Score(s):** Wisdom, Constitution  
**Power Fantasy:** You've lived with sickness and injury so long that you've become an expert at treating yourself—and that hard-won knowledge makes you exceptionally effective at healing and purging ailments in others.  
**Design Notes:** Resource-driven support with short-rest recovery; focus on healing, condition removal, disease resistance, and turning personal affliction into curative power.

---

